    <p>Sin­gapo(ren): Dis­cov­er­ing Chi­nese Sin­ga­porean Cul­ture</p>
    <p>The Sin­ga­pore Chi­nese Cul­tural Cen­tre re­opens its in­au­gu­ral per­ma­nent ex­hi­bi­tion, which high­lights how Chi­nese her­itage, cul­tural in­ter­ac­tions and pub­lic poli­cies have shaped Chi­nese cul­ture in Sin­ga­pore and evolved in ways that are dif­fer­ent from other Chi­nese com­mu­ni­ties in other parts of the world.</p>
    <p>Sin­ga­pore Chi­nese Cul­tural Cen­tre,</p>
    <p>1 Straits Boule­vard Tan­jong Pa­gar</p>
    <p>Mon, 2 - 8pm; Tues to Sun, 10am - 8pm</p>
    <p>Free sin­ga­poreccc.org.sg</p>


